Specifying that his raids (and subsequent rule) were confined to North India (which in this case includes pakistan). For eg, The Deep-South of India and even the nearer South and thus the entire South Zone, as well as the Northeast Zone had zilch to do with ghazni's transgressions (as was the case with almost any muslim polity in the medieval period). Also he did not get to attack other well-known urban centers of North India like Ayodhya and Gaya.
